features: Magnetic Tiles Starter Kit: Our magnetic tiles set including 42 pcs of magnetic pieces, exquisite packaging, and a creative book. The magnetic building tiles come in vibrant colors with high transparency. When placed under sunlight or with a light in the center during nighttime, they create beautiful rainbow-like shadows. This magnetic toy set is compatible with most magnetic tiles available in the market, keeping your child engaged and away from electronic games.

Strong Magnets: DMOIU magnetic tiles feature larger dimensions and stronger magnetic force, allowing for the construction of more intricate structures. They provide parents with a relaxing experience during focused thinking and organizing tasks. Playing together with parents enhances the parent-child relationship, while joining peers in model toy puzzle games fosters teamwork. It's an inspiring and entertaining toy gift!

Safe Material: Designed with safety and durability, this magnetic toy set is made of high-quality ABS material with built-in powerful magnets in each tile. The building tiles have a durable, smooth, and flat surface, allowing your child to build structures wider and higher without limitations. They also serve as great toys for imaginative playtime, easily matching various character figures, toy cars, and other toys in your home. It's a wonderful educational toys gift for boys and girls!

Versatile Usage: This magnetic tile toy is not only a good educational resource for school classrooms, kindergartens, and daycare centers but also an excellent toy for children's party activities and game days. It's a magical children's toy suitable for toddlers, preschoolers, and school-aged children, even loved by teenagers. It also makes for a perfect holiday gift, and your child will be pleasantly surprised to receive it on occasions like Halloween, Christmas, New Year, birthdays, and more.

After-Sales Service: Our goal is to provide high-quality products and impeccable customer service. If there are any quality issues, please contact us, and we will take full responsibility and provide you with a satisfactory solution.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Translucent brightly colored and basic geometric shapes easily connect for open-ended, constructive play!

Colorful Clear 3D Magnetic Building Blocks - Bonding by playing, fun for all age! STEM Learning With DMOIU magnetic building tiles, children can develop so many skills such as hand-eye coordination, fine motor skills, problem-solving skills, and learn concepts such as cause and effect. DMOIU magnet tiles help children master the basic knowledge of geometry, construction, 3D forms, and develop kids' imagination, creativity, spatial thinking, and logical ability.

FEATURES Larger and Stronger Magnet DMOIU magnetic tiles comes with larger magnets and provide stronger magnetism, which can help your kids to build larger and more complicated structures. High transparency Different random colors of magnetic blocks with high transparency. The light will be throught the blocks and project a beautiful colorful shadow on the floor. Perfect Gift for Any Occasion DMOIU magnetic tiles set comes with beautiful gift box and idea book, it will be a big surprise to your kids when given as a Birthday or Christmas gift!

Magnetic Tiles About DMOIU DMOIU is driven by its goal of making toys the source of children's happiness, and we meet that goal by providing innovative, safe, and quality products. As a professional toy manufacturer, we design and produce qualified toys for children of many developmental stages.
